JSON Wire Protocol ek communication protocol tha jo Selenium me test script aur browser driver ke beech communication ke liye use hota tha.

Simple words me:
Yeh Selenium commands ko JSON format me convert karke HTTP request ke through browser driver ko send karta tha.
--------------------------------------
How JSON Wire Protocol Works

Flow kuch is tarah hota tha:

Test Script
     ↓
Selenium Client Library
     ↓
JSON Wire Protocol (JSON + HTTP request)
     ↓
Browser Driver (ChromeDriver / GeckoDriver)
     ↓
Browser
----------------------------------
JSON Wire Protocol is a communication protocol used in Selenium to send commands from the test script to the browser driver in JSON format over HTTP. 
It was used in Selenium 3, but in Selenium 4 it has been replaced by the W3C WebDriver Protocol.
